{
  "stem": "11274.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The floor was just-- on the first floor where they were living there, and said, you get dress quickly and  you run to the Kornreichs, and you tell them that-- to hide Rena.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- tell them a German officer is looking for her [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's drunk and god knows what he's going to do to her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he got dressed they went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the officer is sitting there, but because he was drunk, the father was trying to-- he said, what is taking him so long?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, he's asleep, a hard sleeper, and a very slowpoke to dressing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He is dressing, he'll be here any minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he ran all the way, it wasn't very far, he made it to warn my parents about it, and came back [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in between him coming back, Mother-- Mother had brought me to the attic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we had a farm, we had straw on the whole top floor, there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She brought me to the attic and hid me under-- under the straw, the farthest away from the stairs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And lucky she did, because about five minutes later, they were pounding-- Mom and Dad stayed in their night clothes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they-- when he pounded on the [INAUDIBLE] with the-- with the rifle-- pounded on the door, came-- they both looked sleepy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Danka was hidden under the blankets there in the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and they came out acting sleepy-- what's going on?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We want-- I want Rena.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, she isn't home, she went to the other village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are lying, you dirty Jews, I see if that is true.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know how he made it, because Mom said he was drunk, made it up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From the hallway was a staircase to go to the attic.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
